{"tid":1438663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[必睇][長文]抗爭必勝指引","createTime":"2019-08-09T23:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T00:46:20.000Z","uid":258321,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"158fff874d7e0e3f1fd4cbbd98125cf854025903","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:21:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武同不合作運動係一定要有</span> 但係依家做法可以唔同 一陣下面講<br />\n大家好清醒 喱幾日不停有人講林鄭D陰謀 <br />\n又有好多意見 等我係度整合下 再講下個人建議<br />\n首先，政府做既野其實離唔開幾樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. <span style=\"color: red;\">淡化訴求</span></span><br />\n將焦點spin去警民衝突, 將警民衝突放大,<br />\n話示威者激進攻擊警方, 講到示威者只有氣焰沒有主張, AKA爛仔、搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. <span style=\"color: red;\">醜化示威者</span></span>,<br />\n塑造黑警良好形象 稱示威者為暴徒 控以暴動罪 <br />\n勾結鄉黑將示威者同黑社會毆鬥扯上關係<br />\n係記招將示威者做既野醜化再宣傳<br />\n例如將保護自己唔俾人影而要求del相講成圍困市民、搶手機、非法禁錮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令民眾對我地有負面感觀<br />\n同時黑警做戲扮理性、有禮, 用每日記招將偏頗警方既資訊植入於大眾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. <span style=\"color: red;\">扣港獨帽子</span></span><br />\n話我地搞港獨、革命 俾公眾一個我地會搞亂香港既意識 <br />\n令一大部份對港獨反感既民眾對示威者反感 尤其長輩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. <span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. <span style=\"color: red;\">屈大台</span></span><br />\n近期既民間記者會俾689屈做大台又俾葉國謙屈有大台<br />\n將示威者塑造成被利用、煽惑既傻仔 扭曲輿論<br />\n［港共反攻啦］佢地唔係蠢到以為有大台，佢地係要屈大台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431630</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. <span style=\"color: red;\">經濟下滑論</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n==========================================<br />\n<br />\n跟住 唔該大家諗諗究竟出黎既目的係咩<br />\n撤例、放人、收暴動定性、普選、查黑警 喱堆就哽<br />\n但重點係咩?<br />\n係爭取<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">主櫂、民主</span></strong> 無論咩方法都得<br />\n所以有第一個建議:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong> 不拘於港獨</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">港獨又好, 城邦又好 全部只係方法</span> <br />\n唔好講乜野唯一出路乜乜乜 依家咩係出路無人知 <br />\n我淨係知我想要既係民主 唔一定係獨立<br />\n依家提港獨大眾唔喜歡 不利我地 我地就暫且唔提<br />\n係度懇請各位仲想掛旗 一心堅持港獨既人暫時停止宣揚港獨 我地要既係民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接落黎有人見我提民意 就又會扣民意撚帽子俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係以為真係唔洗理民意呀嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係既話777洗大費周章搞咁多野出黎搞輿論???<br />\n又spin走你又每日記招 你估維穩唔洗錢?<br />\n做人唔好咁極端 話唔理就乜都唔理 <br />\n梁天琦都講 <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>係要令唔支持既人都變成支持我地</strong></span> <br />\n唔理民意 點搞?<br />\n<br />\n所以既然要搞民意搞輿論, 我有以下幾個建議:<br />\n首先, 認清一件事<br />\n心入面幾撚憎黑警、鄉黑都好,<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">表面上做/講所有野都要針對政府</span> AKA 對準政權<br />\n表面啫 實際唔洗 一陣就明<br />\n點解? 因為要營造一個<span style=\"color: red;\">歸咎於政府既風氣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個日塞鑽石山站聽到個呀姨慶過火屎咁講「最衰就係個仆街林鄭, 一早回應D後生仔咪好囉!」<br />\n就係要喱種 地鐵係我地搞塞 俾人鬧既都要係777<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>正文</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方向一 <span style=\"color: blue;\">暴露警方醜態</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警現時策略:<br />\n[黑警戰術] 新官上場, 黃大仙一役已明顯變陣, 各位手足留意<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438314</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點: 挑釁黑警 增加仇恨 引戰 等佢地失控 同時不影響示威者形象</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 挑釁引戰</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>- 言語</strong></span><br />\n狗照撚 用既言語可以更有煽動性 鼓勵大家關心下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如老婆愛唔愛佢地、家人安全有冇受威脅、番十幾個鐘工老婆做緊咩呀<br />\n大家做開匿名打手 相信大家熟過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>注意: 旁門側擊好了 切忌太露骨、有恐嚇等成份 記住唔好影響形象</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>- 弱雞/唔起眼 遠攻先手</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n野照掟 <strong>掟睇落去最無殺傷力/唔起眼既野 先手引黑警失控</strong> 唔洗等打先掟<br />\ne.g. 雞蛋 或者 整啲bottle cap balloon gun射下野<br />\n之前有巴絲po過<br />\nDIY教學:<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gtwGwv-mp9U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgtwGwv-mp9U&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=8b7ca854\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gtwGwv-mp9U</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 散攻集守</span></strong><br />\n黑警打就一定係要打, 諗下當初點解由和平遊行變成依家咁就知<br />\n但係建議集會時大夥係集體防守(當然唔係捱打) 大丫叉、磚個啲盡量同前排散開, 亦可善用天橋等地勢 減低俾人影到 影響形象既機會<br />\n甚至如有手足夠吉屎 拎大丫叉趁機攻擊集會附近狗屋 HIT &amp; RUN<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方向二 <span style=\"color: blue;\">營造示威者正面形象</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. BE HUMBLE</span></strong></span><br />\n時刻守禮、積功德<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 保護者形象, 收割光環</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信黑警打平民既事已經唱到街知巷聞<br />\n唱衰黑警同時 攞個正義光環 講到驅除黑警 保護市民咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>方向三 <span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣/口號</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 五大訴求</span></strong></span><br />\n 一定要將「五大訴求 缺一不可」之類的推番做主流口號 洗走港獨帽子既負面影響 最好加埋插政府既元素 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 暗黑化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n以其人之道還治其人之身, 醜化佢地, 合理化自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點: 將藍絲最唔鍾意既野加番哂落黑警身上, e.g. 亂, 經濟, 民生, 阻搵食, 然後入埋政府數 再攞番D訴求出黎講</span></strong><br />\nE.G.:<br />\n黑警作亂 政府無能<br />\n重組警隊 捍衛市民<br />\n期待大家既發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>行動/文宣方面建議</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 不合作運動</span></strong></span><br />\n好有用 照搞 但注意兩點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">- 利民式</span></strong></span><br />\n上次塞鐵無疑觀感係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家不妨試下搞D大眾唔反對 甚至私下支持既事 e.g. 接放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">香港人鍾意番工 亦鍾意收工</span> 之前稅務大樓個人覺得非常好 可以做多啲<br />\n嫌悶可以搞下其他部門 或 撐警/藍絲企業寫字樓 分分鐘成棟樓一齊放<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>- 持續進行</strong></span></span><br />\n係就唔好搞一次兩次 個個星期都搞 尤其政府部門 長期增加政府運作成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 集會宣傳</span></span></strong><br />\n個人覺得叫人出黎既宣傳可以統一少少 兩三款就好 <br />\n其實中共個種一律紅底白字既文宣係幾勁<br />\n至少可以做到係人都知佢推緊掃黑除惡<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>最後, 鑑於大家好似傻撚左咁聽唔明 不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請盲從以下鐵則:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 無大台<br />\n2. 意見可俾，但不屌不反<br />\n鬼、左膠、爬山方法一律適用 有咩事負皮即可<br />\n3. 反對任何違反以上原則之事</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nP牌任講唔嬲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今次一定要贏 <br />\n民主在望<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f31ff32166776421e08a7ebd88f2c94c0c769404","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"154b64256ab02e1a9620ee4bdfaf9cd2a030ee0b","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:21:58.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"75e70e8fe05ef1fc5e4ce9a3c2be0f70f8243859","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:22:08.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"60f21957ecf4862715a35cb2f5b0092bc05efa3d","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"07004aacb0e984a9383936ad53c671c5108254be","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c980c09757d552275751905d86d3625812082d8","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:22:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfedbb551ae67cd1c0d64e1be1e8750f09247234","tid":1438663,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:24:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47ca4b958bc22ddbb61902006cdd836743881e09","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59f7f3cd60eb83b168046f6d693daddf2e178455","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:25:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dac9129bb005e8bb62877236f42eab832a165b4","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c5d6aa393359e35e557cc111052a21a3a35c72a","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:27:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22702f4124d9d397290b4c58739dd5790f629da8","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:29:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7053434e5112a9177f91b4fa923d7d2ee14ca55d","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:30:33.000Z","msg":"[不合作運動進化－還富於民] 過海隧道免費！！！！！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437617</a>"},{"pid":"22b37a4fc55a7f9181202d05ab96d300906be075","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd28edd4a46c3a9def42828f1e2c4edaaf9b3c8","tid":1438663,"uid":113234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:36:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83613cd585dcd096665cdfe209f64eb09a350a17","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:53:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f759071ef7f0c264d0b89b96a23fbc24008eca5d","tid":1438663,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:55:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a1e0d3e410cdf300f78e44b2679905cd299c06d3","tid":1438663,"uid":255489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:46:20.000Z","msg":"7婆呢招夠哂陰毒!!!!"}]}